Even nicer UX

I'd actually replace the camera icon with:

<span class="k-icon k-i-share"></span>

because users usually interpret it as Export / Share, and the menu:

┌──────────────────────┐
│ 📋 Copy to Clipboard │
│ 🖼 Save as PNG       │
└──────────────────────┘

feels very natural. The button stays tiny and unobtrusive while still being discoverable.
